g.text: - Homepage has Article list (first few chars), paginated with some info
- You can create an account, validate then post articles & comment on them
- Articles do belong to a category that are used to group similar articles
- On clicking an article link -> get article details and comments
- You can list articles by user
- logged in users can fav (like) other users then they can see their articles
- you can search articles based on a keyword
